158985</ingested><modified> 2023-06-07T17:29:52+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[Media]]></category><category><![CDATA[Celebrities]]></category><category><![CDATA[Arts & Entertainment]]></category><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Lawrence Bonk]]></category><media:content height="4024" medium="image" url="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-06/96ab5040-0556-11ee-a6d5-ab519c9fb59c" width="6048"><media:keywords>标题</media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[1]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ ]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[ ]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[ ]]></media:title></media:content><media:content height="4024" medium="image" url="https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-06/96ab5040-0556-11ee-a6d5-ab519c9fb59c" width="6048"><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[2]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[Suzanne Tenner / Lucasfilm Ltd.]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[(L-R): Ahsoka Tano (Rosario Dawson) and Sabine Wren (Natasha Liu Bordizzo) in Lucasfilm's AHSOKA, exclusively on Disney+. Â©2022 Lucasfilm Ltd. & TM. All Rights Reserved.]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[AHSOKA]]></media:title></media:content></item><item><title><![CDATA[How to build a box fan air filter to escape the Canada wildfire smoke]]></title><description type="html"><![CDATA[<p>随着加拿大大规模野火产生的烟雾向大西洋蔓延，东海岸正感受到气候危机的不受欢迎的味道（和气味）。令人回想起<a data-i13n="cpos:1;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/call-duty-vanguard-california-fires-2020-stalingrad-153029085.html">西海岸在 2020 年所经历</a>的一切，本周纽约市上空的天空<a data-i13n="cpos:2;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/what-youll-need-to-survive-the-california-wildfires-this-summer-130008988.html">变成了朦胧的橙色</a>，使<a data-i13n="cpos:3;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/how-to-understand-the-air-quality-index-165633539.html">五个行政区的 AQI 得分跃升</a>。纽约周三被列为<a data-i13n="cpos:4;pos:1" href="https://www.cbsnews.com/news/new-york-city-second-worst-air-quality-in-world-canada-wildfire-smoke/">地球上空气质量第二差的</a>城市，仅次于德里。</p><p>雾霾危害健康，尤其是对任何患有呼吸系统疾病、哮喘、高血压、糖尿病的人，无论是老人还是婴儿。即使您的肺功能正常，也不是很好。幸运的是，我的意思是，从最相对的意义上讲，我们正在摆脱通过气溶胶化呼气传播的全球大流行病的高峰期，因此纽约已经精通在公共场合戴口罩的做法。很好，如果你接下来几天要出门，你将需要这些技能——以及你仍然藏起来的任何 N95。如果有，也可以戴护目镜；细颗粒物是对敏感眼睛的谋杀。</p><span id="end-legacy-contents"></span><p>除非你住在一个密闭的大号玻璃容器中，否则来自外面的朦胧空气最终会进入内部，<a data-i13n="cpos:5;pos:1" href="https://iopscience.iop.org/article/10.1088/2752-5309/ac7d69">颗粒物质可以进一步集中</a>在那里。除非你想在风暴过去之前不停地佩戴 N95，否则你将需要一种方法来过滤公寓中的空气。</p><p>当然，您可以花几百美元购买某个型号——或者您可以凑齐一些胶带、一个箱式风扇和一些不错的老式 American Ingenuity™ 来打造您自己的一个。</p><p>这个项目需要三样东西：</p><ul><li><p>一个盒子风扇：不管多大，不管多旧，不管多便宜，只要确保风扇的边长等于过滤器的长度，所以如果你有一个<a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;cpos:6;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAAfCvwPDIImElT-KCTxgykwroSJC5-B3dVLrGkm7sgk0f&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FAmazon-Basics-Speed-Box-20-Inch%2Fdp%2FB08XKC9K14%2F" class="rapid-with-clickid">20 英寸的箱式风扇</a>，还有<a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;cpos:7;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAAWn9FrDY3bEf0pVj-Vg2tS1gSF7X3mmO517uV-FLd8r2&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FBNX-20x20x1-MERV-Filter-Pack%2Fdp%2FB09XC3RQ3J%2F" class="rapid-with-clickid">20 英寸的过滤器</a>。这样一切都均匀地组合在一起，面板之间不会有奇怪的间隙。</p></li><li><p>四个额定<a data-i13n="cpos:8;pos:1" href="https://www.epa.gov/indoor-air-quality-iaq/what-merv-rating">MERV 13-16</a>或<a data-i13n="cpos:9;pos:1" href="https://www.filtertime.com/news/what-is-the-meaning-of-mpr-fpr-and-merv#:~:text=MPR%20Filter%20Ratings&amp;text=The%20breakdown%20of%20the%20levels,smog%2C%20cough%2C%20and%20sneezes.">MPR 1200-2800 的</a>交流空气过滤器。这些是过滤效率的标准化衡量标准，表明该产品可以有效过滤环境空气中 2.5 微米的烟雾颗粒。如果您选择更高等级的材料，它们甚至会滋生细菌和病毒。</p></li><li><p>胶带： <a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;cpos:10;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiI2NmVhNTY3YS1jOTg3LTRjMmUtYTJmZi0wMjkwNGVmZGU2ZWEiLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYW1hem9uLmNvbS9PcmlnaW5hbC1TdHJlbmd0aC1EdWNrLVNpbHZlci0zOTQ0NzUvZHAvQjAwMDBESDRNRS8_dGFnPWdkZ3QwYy1wLW8tMTIxLTIwIiwiY29udGVudFV1aWQiOiI0YjE4NzYxZC05ZmNiLTQ0NTctOWRiYy02ZjEwMTE5Y2MyYjcifQ&amp;signature=AQAAAas72Wu2_KuIRcvN6g6icX97aAHk7RnzQW5CHEN8eglC&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FOriginal-Strength-Duck-Silver-394475%2Fdp%2FB0000DH4ME%2F" class="rapid-with-clickid">风管品种</a>总是赢家， <a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;cpos:11;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAAWcQpOHmo1fd8H5VVTWYjk-TD1NqGl5xr8UoZvYhXPD4&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FScotchBlue-Original-Multi-Surface-Painters-inches%2Fdp%2FB00004Z4DU%2F" class="rapid-with-clickid">蓝色油漆工胶带</a>也不错。</p></li></ul><p>要构建它，请将每个过滤器的末端与其相邻过滤器成直角放置，以便所有四个过滤器都形成一个正方形，每个过滤器上的箭头指示器朝内。将它们全部粘在一起，形成这种形状，确保不要用胶带覆盖实际的过滤器位。将风扇放在顶部，以便将空气吹入您刚刚制作的正方形并用胶带固定。插上电源就可以了。有趣的事实：这对于掩盖宿舍里故意产生的烟味也有奇效，但我不会有这种恶作剧的经验。</p>本文最初出现在 Engadget 上，网址为 https://www.engadget.com/how-to-build-a-box-fan-air-filter-to-escape-the-canada-wildfire-smoke-172043312.html?src =rss]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/how-to-build-a-box-fan-air-filter-to-escape-the-canada-wildfire-smoke-172043312.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> 4b18761d-9fcb-4457-9dbc-6f10119cc2b7</guid><dc:creator>安德鲁·塔兰托拉</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher>Engadget</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder> Engadget</dc:rightsholder><pubDate> Wed, 07 Jun 2023 17:20:43 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1686160408</ingested><modified> 2023-06-07T17:53:36+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Andrew Tarantola]]></category><media:content height="3850" medium="image" url="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-06/f1908fe0-0536-11ee-b6ee-b6a94b552673" width="5923"><media:keywords>标题</media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[1]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ ]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[ ]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[ ]]></media:title></media:content><media:content height="3850" medium="image" url="https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-06/f1908fe0-0536-11ee-b6ee-b6a94b552673" width="5923"><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[2]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[Gary Hershorn via Getty Images]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[JERSEY CITY, NJ - JUNE 7: Smoke continues to shroud the sun as it rises behind the skyline of lower Manhattan and One World Trade Center in New York City on June 7, 2023, as seen from Jersey City, New Jersey.  (Photo by Gary Hershorn/Getty Images)]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[Smokey Sunrise in New York City]]></media:title></media:content></item><item><title><![CDATA[Samsung's Galaxy S23 series is on sale for as low as $700 right now]]></title><de